"I do not wish a =
conflict with you either but it is our custom to bear our arms in a show of=
 respect for each others full strength." the trainer held his arms forward =
holding his constrictor rifle and revealing his shoulder and leg mounted ro=
cket launchers. He knew there was no such custom but his scanners were read=
